You will need the KCWI r-band spectra, plus the variance spectra, to measure the integrated velocity dispersion.
This can be found using the accompanying Google Drive folder (via https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1_0nJ4VX7Si8bvLCUX6HnJ4QlTc93IeL4?usp=sharing).
The flux cube is "DESJ2112_integrated_defl_r.fits" and the variance "DESJ2112_integrated_var_r.fits". 
